videos.description: Justin Robinson knocks down the 3-pointer off the window for Duke.
videos.headline: Duke's Robinson banks in the 3-pointer

videos.description: Cole Anthony gets the tough layup to fall, but North Carolina doesn't get back as Cassius Stanley flushes home the two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony and Stanley exchange impressive buckets) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Anthony and Stanley exchange impressive buckets

videos.description: Tre Jones throws the beautiful backdoor pass to Cassius Stanley for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones drops dime to Stanley for the layup) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Jones drops dime to Stanley for the layup

videos.description: Former Duke stars including Grant Hill and Christian Laettner are in attendance at the rivalry matchup against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Former Duke stars in attendance

videos.description: Wendell Moore Jr. gets out in transition and throws the perfect bounce pass to Tre Jones for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Moore threads the needle to Jones for the layup) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Moore threads the needle to Jones for the layup

videos.description: North Carolina's Jeremiah Francis knocks down the wide-open jumper cutting Duke's lead to 8 at the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Francis hits the jumper before the half cutting into Duke's lead) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Francis hits the jumper before the half cutting into Duke's lead

videos.description: Justin Robinson blocks the shot which leads to Vernon Carey Jr. flushing home the transition dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Robinson's block lead to the Carey dunk) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Robinson's block lead to the Carey dunk

videos.description: Cole Anthony looks like he travelled, but it isn't called and Garrison Brooks ends up getting the tough floater to fall.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_one-Play (Brooks puts in the tough shot, after Anthony appears to get away with a travel) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Brooks puts in the tough shot, after Anthony appears to get away with a travel

videos.description: Justin Robinson gets the roll on the 3-pointer, prompting his dad, NBA hall of famer David Robinson to celebrate.

tracking.trackingName: NCB One-Play (David Robinson hyped after his son hits the 3) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: David Robinson hyped after his son hits the 3

videos.description: Tre Jones comes off the screen and finds Vernon Carey Jr. who lays it in through the defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones throws the lob to Carey for the layup) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Jones throws the lob to Carey for the layup

videos.description: Justin Robinson on senior night gets the Cameron Crazies roaring with his 4th 3-pointer of the night.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Robinson hits his fourth 3 of the night) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: Robinson hits his fourth 3 of the night

videos.description: NBA legend David Robinson talks about how proud he is of his son Justin, who scored 13 points on his senior night vs. North Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (David Robinson glowing after his son's performance on senior night) 2020/03/07

videos.headline: David Robinson glowing after his son's performance on senior night

videos.description: After North Carolina cut the score to 44-43, Duke gets contributions up and down the roster, with Justin Robinson scoring 13 points, and pulls away for a 89-76 win vs. UNC.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Duke pulls away to sweep UNC ) 2020/03/07 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Duke pulls away to sweep UNC
